<tr>
<td colspan=2>
<input type="submit" name="$prefsPage.actionBarUpName" value="Move up">
<input type="submit" name="$prefsPage.actionBarDelName" value="Delete">
</td>
</tr>

</table>

## addbar
<table>
<tr>
<th colspan=4 align=left>Add new section</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>$prefsPage.addBarTitle</td>
<td>
